execution/agents/library/meta/missionary/strategy-002-navier-stokes-learnings.md:32:3. **C(F₄) direction should have been killed before becoming a strategy direction.** The algebraic identity C_Leff⁴ = F₄ · R³ is trivially derivable from the definitions. The missionary (me) should have checked this before including it as Direction B. **Missionary should computationally verify key empirical claims from prior strategies before building the next strategy around them.** A 5-minute sub-agent computation would have caught this.
